{
  "texts": [
    "This dataset aims to fill the gap left by existing relation extraction datasets, which are predominantly compiled from general sources like Wikipedia or news articles.",
    "For evaluation, we prompted the language models to output the relation of an entity pair given the sentence and entity pairs.",
    "We did not count no relationship entity pairs.",
    "The REFinD dataset is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0) License.",
    "The Zero-Shot prompt used for ReFinD is given in Figure 14."
  ]
}